```plantuml
@startuml darrenyao87_tnn-models

package "HiAI DDK" {
    [HiAiModelManagerService] as ModelManager
    [HiAiAippPara] as AIPP
    [NativeHandle] as Memory
    [AiTensor] as Tensor
    [TensorDimension] as TensorDim
}

package "TNN Framework" {
    [TNNModel] as Model
    [TNNProto] as Proto
    [RapidProto] as RapidP
    [RapidModel] as RapidM
}

package "Model Types" {
    [ObjectDetection] as ObjDetect
    [FaceDetection] as FaceDetect
    [OCR] as OCR
    [BERT] as BERT
    [ImageSegmentation] as Seg
    [PoseEstimation] as Pose
    [ImageTranslation] as ImgTrans
}

package "Supporting Data" {
    [vocab.txt] as Vocab
    [keys.txt] as Keys
    [anchors.txt] as Anchors
}

ModelManager --> AIPP : configures
ModelManager --> Memory : manages
ModelManager --> Tensor : handles
Tensor --> TensorDim : uses
ModelManager --> Model : loads

Model --> Proto : structure
Model --> RapidP : optimized
Model --> RapidM : weights

Model --> ObjDetect
Model --> FaceDetect
Model --> OCR
Model --> BERT
Model --> Seg
Model --> Pose
Model --> ImgTrans

OCR --> Keys : uses
BERT --> Vocab : uses
FaceDetect --> Anchors : uses

@enduml
```